battle with demons 900 years ago in the divine

various places and over a long period of time, it
came to be recognized as a power to counter
demons.

and those who cannot is said to be determined by
the amount of magical power they are born with.

Magic is used by utilizing magical power. Magical
power exists not only within the body, but also in
the atmosphere.

There are places where magical power is
concentrated, and generally, it tends to become
stronger as you go underground.
